[
    {
        "text": "A Brighter Future.",
        "startTime": 749,
        "endTime": 2181,
        "slowStartTime": 1274,
        "slowEndTime": 3497
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you think futurists can really predict what's going to happen?",
        "startTime": 2930,
        "endTime": 5918,
        "slowStartTime": 4545,
        "slowEndTime": 9102
    },
    {
        "text": "In fact, \"futurists\" don't predict the future.",
        "startTime": 6361,
        "endTime": 9004,
        "slowStartTime": 9692,
        "slowEndTime": 13731
    },
    {
        "text": "Instead, they pay a great deal of attention to trends and issues that will impact our future.",
        "startTime": 9552,
        "endTime": 14406,
        "slowStartTime": 14478,
        "slowEndTime": 21834
    },
    {
        "text": "They then ask people to consider the implications of those trends and issues...",
        "startTime": 15087,
        "endTime": 19099,
        "slowStartTime": 22780,
        "slowEndTime": 28873
    },
    {
        "text": "...for their business, industry, profession, government, or country, for themselves or for the world.",
        "startTime": 19360,
        "endTime": 24649,
        "slowStartTime": 29190,
        "slowEndTime": 37198
    },
    {
        "text": "As your family, group, or organization makes plans for the future,...",
        "startTime": 25674,
        "endTime": 29275,
        "slowStartTime": 38661,
        "slowEndTime": 44137
    },
    {
        "text": "...they need to see themselves in context.",
        "startTime": 29733,
        "endTime": 31784,
        "slowStartTime": 44749,
        "slowEndTime": 47901
    },
    {
        "text": "They must consider the political, economic, social, technological, environmental,...",
        "startTime": 32302,
        "endTime": 36941,
        "slowStartTime": 48603,
        "slowEndTime": 55636
    },
    {
        "text": "...demographic changes, and other forces that are likely to impact them.",
        "startTime": 37256,
        "endTime": 41042,
        "slowStartTime": 56034,
        "slowEndTime": 61788
    },
    {
        "text": "Likewise,...",
        "startTime": 41728,
        "endTime": 42329,
        "slowStartTime": 62742,
        "slowEndTime": 63718
    },
    {
        "text": "...they try to imagine how things will change because of those different forces working together...",
        "startTime": 42740,
        "endTime": 47562,
        "slowStartTime": 64260,
        "slowEndTime": 71568
    },
    {
        "text": "...or against each other.",
        "startTime": 47860,
        "endTime": 48887,
        "slowStartTime": 71940,
        "slowEndTime": 73556
    },
    {
        "text": "We might call those who pay attention to trends and issues as being \"in touch\".",
        "startTime": 49750,
        "endTime": 53765,
        "slowStartTime": 74775,
        "slowEndTime": 80872
    },
    {
        "text": "Those who don't are usually called \"out of touch\".",
        "startTime": 54075,
        "endTime": 56653,
        "slowStartTime": 81263,
        "slowEndTime": 85205
    },
    {
        "text": "Rather than flying blind, futurists help us see the airspace in front of us.",
        "startTime": 57137,
        "endTime": 61208,
        "slowStartTime": 85856,
        "slowEndTime": 92037
    },
    {
        "text": "They can help us develop scenarios and...",
        "startTime": 61789,
        "endTime": 63687,
        "slowStartTime": 92834,
        "slowEndTime": 95756
    },
    {
        "text": "...test our assumptions about the nature of the future.",
        "startTime": 63825,
        "endTime": 66457,
        "slowStartTime": 95888,
        "slowEndTime": 99911
    },
    {
        "text": "The World Future Society...",
        "startTime": 67264,
        "endTime": 68675,
        "slowStartTime": 101046,
        "slowEndTime": 103238
    },
    {
        "text": "...plays a key role in bringing people \"in touch\" with the future and together from many disciplines,...",
        "startTime": 69075,
        "endTime": 74247,
        "slowStartTime": 103763,
        "slowEndTime": 111595
    },
    {
        "text": "...ranging from education and medicine to technology and security...",
        "startTime": 74473,
        "endTime": 77967,
        "slowStartTime": 111859,
        "slowEndTime": 117175
    },
    {
        "text": "...help others see what the future may be like.",
        "startTime": 78279,
        "endTime": 80599,
        "slowStartTime": 117568,
        "slowEndTime": 121123
    }
]